channel.title: Interleaved RSS Feed
channel.description: This is an interleaved feed of the most recent entries from each RSS source, skipping any feeds with errors.

item.title: Calgary Wild FC Become First NSL Club to Officially Unveil Name, Logo
item.description: Northern Super League just announced the league name and logo earlier this week; will take to the pitch for inaugural season in 2025

item.title: Matt Rife Apologizes for Having to Cancel Sold-Out Comedy Shows Last Minute
item.description: A bunch of Indianans missed out on comedy shows from Matt Rife this week -- this after he abruptly canceled two sold-out gigs ... something he says he's very sorry about. The comic was scheduled to perform 2 comedy shows Wednesday in Bloomington,…

item.title: Counterfeit Soccer Kit Seller Ordered to Repay £118K or Face Prison
item.description: Seller pled guilty to unauthorized possession and distribution of trademarks in May 2022 after investigation uncovered fakes in 2019 and 2020

item.title: Baylor Bears Unveil New Anthracite Alternate Football Uniforms
item.description: Just two days after it unveiled new green home, white road and gold alternate uniforms, Baylor revealed a new anthracite alternate design on Thursday morning.

item.title: Illinois To Celebrate Memorial Stadium’s 100th Anniversary With Throwback Helmets
item.description: Illinois will celebrate the 100th anniversary of Memorial Stadium by wearing three different throwback helmets during select games this fall.
